Title:
CIPS CFA to specify the structural relationship among three latent variables and
their indicators; Wald Test of Parameter Constraints to test the significance of
a regression estimate for two groups of Imprisoned Parents;
DATA:
FILE IS C:\Users\Oxana\Documents\CIPS2.csv;
VARIABLE:
NAMES ARE idorig CombSiSp YearProg ParentIn PALS alphknow sightwrd spell
numbers geometry measures selfcont cooperat social initiat persist probsolv
PIcat InToNeed gender AdultFam FamSize ethnicit caregiv educatPC ChildFam;
USEVARIABLES ARE YearProg ParentIn CombSiSp PALS alphknow numbers geometry measures
selfcont cooperat social initiat;
MISSING ARE ALL (-99);
GROUPING IS ParentIn (0=NonImprF 1=ImprFath);
MODEL:
! Measurement model (CFAs)
Math by numbers geometry measures;
Literacy by PALS alphknow CombSiSp;
SocSkill by selfcont cooperat social initiat;
Math on YearProg; 
Literacy on YearProg;
SocSkill on YearProg;
Math with Literacy SocSkill;
Literacy with SocSkill;
MODEL NonImprF :
Math on YearProg (p1); 
MODEL ImprFath :
Math on YearProg (p2); 
OUTPUT: STANDARDIZED;
MODEL TEST:
p1=p2;